#   Beagle the SCM

This is the JavaScript implementation of Beagle SCM.
The only dependency is [JAB][j] the JavaScript runtime.
Symlink/mv this as a `be/` dir in cwd or any higher dir 
(e.g. `$HOME/be/). Jab will pick it up.

See the [wiki][w] and guides for [usage patterns][u]. 
This implementation is TUI-centric, any command opens
a pager.

All the heavy-lifting is done by [libdog][d] through
JAB bindings. So, if this set of command does not suit 
you, then complain to Claude, and please share the results.

[j]: https://github.com/gritzko/jab/
[u]: https://replicated.wiki/meta/work
[w]: https://replicated.wiki/wiki/Verbs
[d]: https://github.com/gritzko/libdog
